This gauge layer is the first bridge from pure geometry to field‑like behaviour — curvature is no longer an abstract possibility, but a measurable quantity.

4.3.x — Maxwell Map Discipline
With metric and connection in place, we can embed physical‑law‑like invariants directly into the geometry.

